7.1
  1) I work hard. And you? Do you work hard?
  2) I play tennis. And you? Do you play tennis?
  3) I play tennis. Does Ann play tennis?
  4) I know the answer. Do you know the asnwer?
  5) I like hot weather. Do you like the asnwer?
  6) I smoke. Does your father smoke?
  7) I do exercises every morning. Do you do exercises every morning?
  8) I speak English. Do your friends speak English?
  9) I want to be famous. Do you want to be famous?
  10) I wash my hair twice a week. How often do you wash your hair?
  11) I live in London. Where do you live?
  12) I watch TV every day. How often do you watch TV?
  13) I have lunch at home. Where do you have lunch?
  14) I get up at 7.30. What time do you get up?
  15) I go to the cinema a lot. How often do you go to the cinema?
  16) I go to work by bus. How do you go to work?  
  
7.2 
  1) Does he often play volleyball?
  2) Excuse me, Do you know English?
  3) What do you do?
  4) What does your sister do?
  5) Does she smoke?
  6) How often does it rain in summer?
  7) Do you love dancing?
  8) What time do they usually go to bed?
  9) What do you usually have for breakfast?
  10) How much does it cost to stay at this hotel?
  
7.3
  1) Do you smoke? No, I don't.
  2) Do you live in a big city? Yes, I do.
  3) Do you drink a lot of coffee? No, I don't.
  4) Does your mother speak English? No, She doesn't.
  5) Do you play a musical instrument? Yes, I do.
  6) Does it rain a lot where you live? Yes, It does.
